00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:37.400
Any understanding of Christianity has to start
with Judaism, because Jesus was born a Jew,

00:00:37.410 --> 00:00:40.960
and he grew up in the Jewish tradition. He
was one of many teachers spreading his ideas

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.710
in the Roman province of Judea at the time,
and he was part of a messianic tradition that

00:00:44.710 --> 00:00:49.809
helps us understand why he was thought of
not only teacher but something much, much more.

00:00:49.809 --> 00:00:51.410
